331
00:17:38,930 --> 00:17:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The childhood friend and the homewrecker.</font>

332
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

333
