336
00:17:52,970 --> 00:17:55,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe they're just plain friends.</font>

337
00:17:55,180 --> 00:17:58,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right! I'm sure they're just plain friends!</font>

338
00:17:58,610 --> 00:18:01,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew you'd get it, Yana-chan!</font>

339
00:18:01,430 --> 00:18:05,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lemon-chan, I kinda feel like 
